results.deck: Frogwares was founded in 2000. They are dedicated to making adventure games, and have done so with the the long running Sherlock Holmes series.
results.description:
The development team at Frogwares is over 60 people. They have two studios, one in Ireland, and one in Kiev, Ukraine.

They are currently working on new Sherlock Holmes games, including one for the Wii.

As well as this, they are developing a F2P MMORTS known as World of Battles.
